to run it in RStudio, but RStudio console is blocked. I have to run it over here. Because

00:15:53.200 --> 00:16:00.200
this one is driven by later. This is... You can get a view into the headless browser.

00:16:00.799 --> 00:16:05.280
And then you can sort of interact with it here. I can click on randomize over there.

00:16:05.280 --> 00:16:12.280
And then if I take a screenshot of it again, you'll see that... Sorry. I did it again.

00:16:13.320 --> 00:16:20.320
Okay. If I take a screenshot again, you'll see that that button is sort of grayed, which

